snippet.title: Super Flipman Adventure World Game Play Trailer @Buildboxcom #indiegame #indiedev
snippet.description:
Super Flipman Adventure World
Collect all the Diamonds to unlock next levels and finally release your buddies, Papy and Robo .
Finish 1st World will send you directly to bonus level where you have the chance to  unlock and release Papy .
Finish 2nd World will send you directly to second bonus level where you have the chance to  unlock and release Robo .
Finish 3rd World will send you directly to 3rd bonus level and finally unlock all worlds, all levels, all friends .
You must fight against most scary and dangerous enemies.
The worlds start to be more excitement, shooting worlds,more Diamonds, hidden Diamonds, hidden Enemies,  more Enemies, and much more .

Download Android - https://goo.gl/er6gTI
Download IOS  - https://goo.gl/Xz2wX2
